  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Changes to the delivery of our services during the coronavirus pandemic
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">As a result of government instructions to stay at home we have changed the way we deliver our services.</p>

  </div>
</div>

